Cook pasta as directed on package; omitting salt. Heat Simmer Sauce in large skillet over medium-high heat. Add shrimp; cook and stir 3-5 min. or until shrimp turn pink. Add anchovies, olives, crushed red pepper, and Finishing Sauce. Simmer 3 min. Place pasta in large bowl. Add shrimp mixture; mix lightly. Sprinkle with parsley.